{"tid":310910,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[王者榮耀] 支那童:「怎麼不會飛啊？」 杭州13歲玩家跳樓嚴重骨折","createTime":"2017-07-06T07:37:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T11:43:05.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1766ba425941b78938db02f0ff0897691d08a873","tid":310910,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:37:27.000Z","msg":"「怎麼不會飛啊？」杭州13歲學生張林（化名）6月22日從住宅4樓的天台跳下，造成嚴重骨折，但他倒地一刻還自言自語說，「怎麼不會飛啊？要知道這麼高我就不跳了。」張父事後估計他是模仿遊戲中的角色。<br />\n<br />\n張父上周四接受內地傳媒訪問，講述當時情況。他說當晚兩父子正在家吃飯，其間教訓了張林幾句，勸他少玩《王者榮耀》，張林便突然衝到天台，父親緊追其後，「他看了我一眼突然跳了下去」，惟男童在醫院甦醒後，第一件事竟要求登錄遊戲。"},{"pid":"04c250812fec915324ad6ffe5c2ed2b635516eed","tid":310910,"uid":123712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"符合國情"},{"pid":"c8a402cea5192e8bddb9945cf51b21b2a0844e76","tid":310910,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb34148321f09244cae62fc358c6c2dafe211108","tid":310910,"uid":123712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"那一個可 發育正常"},{"pid":"2f4a782d943c923414ee5eb5bb49b718a799024f","tid":310910,"uid":89696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/cb647cdef6f48e58ec412ac91472c575/tumblr_inline_o71g1cL4WX1tsf0j9_400.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2Fcb647cdef6f48e58ec412ac91472c575%2Ftumblr_inline_o71g1cL4WX1tsf0j9_400.gif&h=540973e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a457a2ee018a449d4bb2c69e626cebbe6dfc0d47","tid":310910,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53bef285d5bfb11b0b1d3e8629fd173d81c158b1","tid":310910,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T07:42:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.wanhuajing.com/pic/1601/1705/4244186/6_356_200